writer\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%C2%BFQue_es_un_plan_de_recuperacion_ante_desastres\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">¿Qué es un plan de recuperación ante desastres?</span><span data-range-char-type=\"start\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Toc6ba8ac8p3mta&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_4nuti2tqwi2x&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;,&quot;render_type&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;geo_transformation&quot;:{&quot;translation&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;scaling&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;rotation&quot;:false}}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_4nuti2tqwi2x\"> </span><span data-range-char-type=\"end\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Toc6ba8ac8p3mta&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_4nuti2tqwi2x&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_4nuti2tqwi2x\"> </span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 12pt 0px; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;12.00&quot;,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-bottom=\"12pt\" data-margin-top=\"12pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">Un </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">DRP (Disaster Recovery Plan) </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; letter-spacing: 0pt; vertical-align: baseline; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">ó </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">plan de recuperación ante desastres</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> es un conjunto de estrategias, procesos y herramientas diseñadas para restaurar rápidamente los sistemas y datos críticos tras incidentes como fallos de hardware, ciberataques o desastres naturales. Gracias a un DRP, tu empresa garantiza la continuidad operativa y evita costos masivos por tiempo de inactividad.</span></p><h3 style=\"margin: 14.94pt 0px; line-height: 1.2;\" data-header=\"2\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-bottom=\"14.94pt\" data-margin-top=\"14.94pt\" data-hd-info=\"2\" data-line-height=\"1.2\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"DRP_vs_BCP_%C2%BFCual_es_la_diferencia\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">DRP vs. BCP: ¿Cuál es la diferencia?</span><span data-range-char-type=\"start\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Tocp9izvwo4awqi&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_wfvnbw40vu8m&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;,&quot;render_type&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;geo_transformation&quot;:{&quot;translation&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;scaling&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;rotation&quot;:false}}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_wfvnbw40vu8m\"> </span><span data-range-char-type=\"end\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Tocp9izvwo4awqi&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_wfvnbw40vu8m&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_wfvnbw40vu8m\"> </span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><p style=\"margin: 12pt 0px; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;12.00&quot;,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-bottom=\"12pt\" data-margin-top=\"12pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">Aunque ambos buscan mantener la continuidad del negocio, el </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">plan de recuperación ante desastres</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> (DRP) se centra exclusivamente en la infraestructura de TI y la restauración de datos. En cambio, un plan de continuidad de negocio (BCP) abarca además procesos comerciales, comunicaciones y logística. </span><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://www.deltaprotect.com/blog/que-es-un-drp\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">El DRP es, </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-size: 12pt; vertical-align: baseline;\">por tanto, un componente esencial dentro del BCP.</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 14.94pt 0px; line-height: 1.2;\" data-header=\"2\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;12.00&quot;,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-bottom=\"14.94pt\" data-margin-top=\"14.94pt\" data-hd-info=\"2\" data-line-height=\"1.2\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Beneficios_de_implementar_un_plan_de_recuperacion_ante_desastres\"></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">Beneficios de implementar un plan de recuperación ante desastres</span><span data-range-char-type=\"start\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Toc8ve529r3cnoq&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_dujxrwcykrzh&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;,&quot;render_type&quot;:&quot;inline&quot;,&quot;geo_transformation&quot;:{&quot;translation&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;scaling&quot;:{&quot;x&quot;:false,&quot;y&quot;:false},&quot;rotation&quot;:false}}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_dujxrwcykrzh\"> </span><span data-range-char-type=\"end\" data-bookmark-info=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;_Toc8ve529r3cnoq&quot;,&quot;id&quot;:&quot;toc_dujxrwcykrzh&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bookmark&quot;}\" data-bookmark-id=\"toc_dujxrwcykrzh\"> </span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"></span></h3><ul style=\"list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;\" data-list-id=\"69548838\" data-list-format=\"{&quot;level5&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:8,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level4&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:7,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level7&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:7,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level6&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:6,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level8&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:8,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level1&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:7,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level0&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:6,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level3&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:6,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1},&quot;level2&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:8,&quot;startsWith&quot;:1}}\" data-spl-bullet-format=\"{}\"><li><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:11,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-left=\"0.5in\" data-text-indent=\"-0.25in\" data-margin-bottom=\"0pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\" data-list-id=\"69548838\" data-list-info=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;69548838&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">Reducción del tiempo de inactividad:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> Un DRP bien definido acorta el tiempo de interrupción, evitando pérdidas económicas significativas.</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:11,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-left=\"0.5in\" data-text-indent=\"-0.25in\" data-margin-bottom=\"0pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\" data-list-id=\"69548838\" data-list-info=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;69548838&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">Protección de datos críticos:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> Garantiza</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> backups</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> fiables y seguros, con objetivos claros de RPO (Recovery Point Objective) y RTO (Recovery Time Objective).</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:11,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-left=\"0.5in\" data-text-indent=\"-0.25in\" data-margin-bottom=\"0pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\" data-list-id=\"69548838\" data-list-info=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;69548838&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">Cumplimiento normativo:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> Muchas industrias (finanzas, salud) exigen un plan de recuperación ante desastres para certificaciones y auditorías.</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0pt; line-height: 1.2; direction: ltr;\" data-header=\"0\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fgc&quot;:&quot;rgb(0, 0, 0)&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:11,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-left=\"0.5in\" data-text-indent=\"-0.25in\" data-margin-bottom=\"0pt\" data-hd-info=\"0\" data-line-height=\"1.2\" data-list-id=\"69548838\" data-list-info=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;69548838&quot;,&quot;l&quot;:0}\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline;\">Mejora de la reputación:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline;\"> Demuestra a clientes y proveedores que tu empresa está preparada ante cualquier contingencia.</span></p></li></ul><div><span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: Open Sans;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\"> </span></span></div><p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12pt; line-height: 1.2;\" data-textformat=\"{&quot;ff&quot;:&quot;Open Sans&quot;,&quot;fw_i&quot;:400,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}\" data-margin-bottom=\"12pt\" data-line-height=\"1.2\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: italic;\">También te interesaría leer:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; color: #000000; font-size: 11pt; font-style: italic;\"> </span><a style=\"color: #0000ff;\" href=\"https://lumacloud.co/cual-es-el-mejor-backup-para-tu-empresa/\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Open Sans'; font-